title: Why Google is ‘re-thinking’ all of its products
text:
Why Google is ‘re-thinking’ all of its products 
Times of India Friday 23rd October, 2015 
• Machine learning and AI got a lot of attention on Google's Q3 earnings call 
• CEO Pichai said Google was "re-thinking" all of its products to include more AI and machine learning 
• At developers' conference earlier this year, Google's smart assistant was miles ahead of Apple's Siri or Microsoft's Cortana...
